{"tid":278780,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那山寨日本新聞節目 連佈景都照抄","createTime":"2017-06-10T17:03:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-11T04:36:28.000Z","uid":43189,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7f14b2eddd4c15f70fa3302edb57e78cce111e49","tid":278780,"uid":43189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T17:03:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpigzuY0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpigzuY0.jpg&h=3d693f87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>中國山寨日本節目 抄好抄滿、連地板都一樣</strong><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國抄襲案例層出不窮，繼日前被控抄襲南韓人氣節目《尹食堂》後，近日又有日本網友發現，有中國節目疑似抄襲日本新聞節目，甚至連攝影棚內的地板設計都一模一樣，讓不少網友直呼誇張。<br />\n<br />\n湖南衛視在2013年推出的新聞節目《今夜iMAX》，疑似抄襲《日本電視台》（NTV）新聞節目《NEWS ZERO》。從照片中可以看到，包括片頭、裝潢、字幕、主持人站位，甚至連地板的設計都幾乎相同。<br />\n<br />\n雖然該節目已經停播，但網友仍留言砲轟：「又是湖南台」、「假設真的是抄襲，那日本告吧，支持維權」、「中國節目就這點出息了嗎」、「被韓國人群嘲完在被日本人嘲」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpFxXosC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpFxXosC.jpg&h=0c976ab3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpP94wy2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpP94wy2.jpg&h=28d03658&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpRJ0VC5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpRJ0VC5.jpg&h=bac4882e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2092212\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2092212&d=P%2BV2fA6K%2BCQ20cZ1qX4pM9tKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=e8a4ecd1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2092212&h=d8ff7853\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2092212</a><br />\n<br />\n日本原報導：<br />\n中国のニュース番組が「NEWS ZERO」とそっくり！パクリ常習犯のテレビ局の盗作か<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.recordchina.co.jp/b180387-s0-c70.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.recordchina.co.jp%2Fb180387-s0-c70.html&d=P%2BV2fA6K%2BCQ20cZ1qX4pM9tKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=855ca9e2\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.recordchina.co.jp/b180387-s0-c70.html</a>"},{"pid":"7379b0d4f7683ed22217e537fdb8316988a8139d","tid":278780,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T17:05:59.000Z","msg":"常習犯"},{"pid":"bdd0d466abdc8381741b56b212e02bdf4e9d2e5f","tid":278780,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T17:08:52.000Z","msg":"支那人 不意外"},{"pid":"2d6a935f7a218c86c182d4d0d07ac2731e6b2e8a","tid":278780,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T18:07:20.000Z","msg":"有無懶d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16960aa2dc0c398fb39c37d5b81ed058871f9f71","tid":278780,"uid":9542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T21:39:35.000Z","msg":"之後屈9架仔抄強國"},{"pid":"8d2601312bbdb1fd16419cb1e45e14dd63a4e4b2","tid":278780,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T22:03:03.000Z","msg":"支那特色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1042f58618072a408d47b520bf349ef3ae660f1e","tid":278780,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T22:20:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f4837e203636bd44b2d5fe738265702cc705a87","tid":278780,"uid":80